iff EoS. This surprising oscillating\nbehavior,a double change of sign of the $v_1$ slope, points to the appearance\nof a hitherto unknown first-order phase transition in excited QCD matter at\nhigh baryon densities in mid-central Au + Au collisions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 8 Jun 2019 23:15:46 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 4 Nov 2019 09:47:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-11-13"}
