ind our occurrence rate method. We\npropose several ways in which confidence in both the Kepler catalog and\noccurrence rate calculations can be improved. This work provides an example of\nhow the community can use the DR25 completeness and reliability products.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 9 Jun 2019 06:01:06 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 20 Jun 2019 02:22:35 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 6 Aug 2019 08:16:38 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Thu, 6 Feb 2020 22:06:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-06-03"}
