rgy loss, the\ndistance, their spin) are derived from observables. The results from the fully\ngeneral-relativistic analysis published in the two discovery papers are\ncompared with the output of our simple treatment. Then, some of the outcomes of\nGW observations are discussed in terms of multimessenger astrophysics.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 9 Jun 2019 14:01:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-06-11"}
