onvolution techniques by large margins both qualitatively (e.g., edge and\ncontrast recovery) and quantitatively (as indicated by two metrics: peak\nsignal-to-noise-ratio and structural similarity index).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 9 Jun 2019 14:15:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-07-29"}
