trary terminations, subject to the condition that WM interfaces are\ndecoupled by the evanescent TM WM mode below the plasma frequency.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 9 Jun 2019 13:40:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-04-22"}
